{
  "stem": "25598.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the one hand, I was a very pampered because I was an only child, and because I was the first [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] grandchild to my grandparents and the first niece to my aunts, who lived in the same town.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So on the one hand, I was spoiled.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on the other hand, I was-- my mother was very, very strict with me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My aunts absolutely adored me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My, my grandmother had three daughters, and that was-- and they were all fantastic as in they were all helping her, because she was a widow.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Her husband died in the First World War, as one of the very few Jewish officers in the Austro-Hungarian army.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I believe my mother was five years old when, when he died.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then the next-- my mother was the oldest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The next one was my Aunt Sidi, who was two years younger than my mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the youngest was my Aunt Mila, who I don't believe ever saw her father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Or I-- it's even possible that my grandmother was-- I think I heard some stories of my that she was born after he was killed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So the last time he was on leave, home, was when my grandmother was pregnant with her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And being left at that time, with, with three girls, was very difficult for my grandmother because you had to prepare dowry.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And also, she was not coming from a rich family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there were no widow's pensions in those times.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The big thing that she got from the government, because she was a war widow, was she was allowed to sell cigarettes and stuff, which was not sold in stores.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
